subject: Request for Training Resources Information
msgSnippet: I am looking for others who are teaching classes on the use of JUnit, Ant and Cactus.  I would appreciated any information you can provide me on organizations
messageBody: I am looking for others who are teaching classes on the use of JUnit, Ant and Cactus.  I would appreciated any information you can provide me on organizations or individuals giving instructor lead training on these technologies (or interested in doing so).  I have identified a lot of learning objectives to pass on in this training.  I would like very much to have more advanced courses to pass my students on to when I have taught them what I know.  Frequently, the students also want on site consulting, so please tell me what you have to offer in that category, should it apply.
